This program is to render the Stanford Bunny using OpenGL with a GLSL shader.

Compiling Instruction: use Makefile

Usage:
	Selectable Eye Point & View Direction:
	- Rotation: Click the left mouse button and drag
	- Zoom in and out: Scroll up and down the mouse wheel
	- Track: Click the right mouse button and drag
	- Focus: Press "f" or "F"

